	<body>
		<category name="Bayonet Enhancements V1.4a by Orudeon">
			<comment>Changes accessories so bayonets never spawn on slot 1, only on slot 2, freeing up your weapon to have a second accessory. Does not despawn existing bayonets on slot 1.</comment>
			<comment>Does not affect certain weapons. Certain guns - mostly uniques and all pearls - now have a guaranteed accessory.</comment>
			<comment>WARNING: This mod alters the fundamental spawning rules of the game. Guns that spawn with a bayonet while this mod is active violate the sanity check. Do not deactivate this mod after using it. Please run this mod as early in your load order as possible.</comment>
			<comment>Coded with assistance from: the_Nocturni, LightChaosman</comment>
			<comment>Any mod that alters WeaponPartListCollectionDefinitions may be incompatible with this.</comment>
			<category name="Extended Description">
				<comment>Example Guns:</comment>
				<comment>Law (Now can have any accessory)</comment>
				<comment>Rubi and Grog Nozzle (Your choice of always has a blade or sometimes has a blade)</comment>
				<comment>Tattler (Now can have any accessory)</comment>
				<comment>Cobra (Always has an accessory)</comment>
				<comment>Pimpernel (Always has an accessory)</comment>
				<comment>Unforgiven (Always spawns with a bayonet)</comment>
			</category>
			<category name="Pistol Bayonets">
				<category name="Accessories">
